        text: "<p>Look at the following chart and answer the question:</p><div class='my-4 flex flex-col items-start gap-2 font-medium'><div class='border-2 border-slate-400 px-4 py-1 rounded bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 ml-4'>Impersonal Account</div><div class='flex gap-0 h-10'><div class='w-10 h-10 border-l-2 border-b-2 border-slate-400 ml-8'></div><div class='border-2 border-slate-400 px-4 py-1 rounded bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 mt-6 ml-2'>Real Account</div></div><div class='flex gap-0 h-10 mt-6'><div class='w-10 h-10 border-l-2 border-b-2 border-slate-400 ml-8'></div><div class='border-2 border-sky-500 border-dashed px-10 py-1 rounded bg-sky-50 dark:bg-sky-900/20 text-sky-600 mt-6 ml-2'>?</div></div></div><p class='mt-10'>Which of the following should be in the '?' marked place?</p>",
