        correctAnswer: 3,
        explanation: "<p>According to the traditional classification of accounts, <strong>Impersonal Accounts</strong> are divided into two categories: <strong>Real Accounts</strong> (related to assets) and <strong>Nominal Accounts</strong> (related to income and expenses).</p>"
