    {
        "id": 247,
        "text": "<p>Mr. Hasan spent 5,000 TK for advertising his furniture business. What is the journal entry? i. Furniture Account-Debit; ii. Advertising Expense Account-Debit; iii. Cash Account-Credit.</p>",
        "meta": "Barishal Board - 2024",
