            "i, ii and iii"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>Promoting a business is a revenue expense. The entry is Advertising Expense Debit. and Cash Credit. Furniture is not debited as it wasn't purchased for use.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 248,
        "text": "<p>What does \"1/10, net/45\" mean? i. 1% discount if paid within 10 days; ii. 1% discount if paid within 45 days; iii. Must Payable within 45 days.</p>",
