        "id": 260,
        "text": "<p>Mr. Samiran's Cash Payment Journal for the month of June 2021 was as follows:\nDate 2021 | Debit (TK) | Reference | Debit (TK) | Debit (TK) | Debit (TK) | Credit (TK) | Credit (TK)\nJune 2 | Purchase | | 5,000 TK | | | 5,000 TK |\nJune 17 | Accounts Payable - Himu | | | 8,000 TK | | 8,000 TK |\nJune 19 | Accounts Payable - Sohag | | | 4,100 TK | | 4,000 TK | 100\nJune 30 | Purchase | | 15,000 TK | | | 15,000 TK |\nTotal | | | 20,000 TK | 12,100 TK | 0 | 32,000 TK | 100\nThe total of Mr. Samiran's Purchase Journal for the month of June was 30,000 TK\nQ: What type of journal is used in the stimulus?</p><div class=\"overflow-x-auto my-4\"><table class=\"min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200 dark:divide-gray-700 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700\"><tr class=\"bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800\"><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Date 2021</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Debit (TK)</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Reference</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Debit (TK)</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Debit (TK)</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Debit (TK)</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left 