            "ii and iii",
            "i, ii and iii"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>When a check is dishonored, the bank balance decreases (Credit Bank) and the debtor's liability is reinstated (Debit Accounts Receivable).</p>"
    },
