    },
    {
        "id": 498,
        "text": "<p>In the \"Adjusted Cash Balance\" (Double-cell) method\u2014i. Both Cash Book & Bank balances are used.ii. Both balances become equal after reconciliation.iii. Correct bank balance is found.</p>",
        "meta": "Dhaka  Board - 2024",
