n-top'><br>2,000</td></tr><tr><td class='border border-gray-300 p-1 align-top'>\" 30</td><td class='border border-gray-300 p-1 text-left'>Loan A/C<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Bank A/C<br><em class='text-[10px] text-gray-500'>(Payment of loan installment by the bank recorded)</em></td><td class='border border-gray-300 p-1'></td><td class='border border-gray-300 p-1 text-right align-top'>6,600</td><td class='border border-gray-300 p-1 text-right align-top'><br>6,600</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>"
