        "explanation": "<p>Posting to the wrong side of the correct account is an Error of Commission (\u09ac\u09c7\u09a6\u09be\u0996\u09bf\u09b2\u09be).</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 736,
        "text": "<p>Preparing a Trial Balance using Ledger balances is called?</p>",
