        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>The Trial Balance is the first step in the Summarizing phase of accounting.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 737,
        "text": "<p>Orpa buys supplies for 950 but records 900 in Supplies Account. Correcting entry?</p>",
        "meta": "Sylhethet  Board - 2022",
