        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Since only the Supplies Account was under-recorded, we use Suspense to balance the correction.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 738,
        "text": "<p>(Ref #110) Due to the error:i. Debit total is 50 shortii. Credit total is 50 moreiii. Suspense needed on Debit side</p>",
