            "i & ii",
            "i & iii",
            "ii & iii",
            "i, ii & iii"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Supplies (Debit) was short, so the total Debit side is short by 50. Suspense fills that gap.</p>"
    },
    {
