        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>25,000 TK+(1,60,000 TK\u22123,000 TK)\u221240,000 TK=1,42,000 TK.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 814,
        "text": "<p>Sale of 1,500 TK recorded as 150. What error?</p>",
