        "options": [
            "Principle",
            "Compensating",
            "Omission",
            "Clerical"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>10k short on Debit and 10k short on Credit cancel out.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 820,
        "text": "<p>(Ref #198) Total Trial Balance sum difference?</p>",
