        "explanation": "<p>100\u00d72=200. When a side is flipped, the gap is double.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 822,
        "text": "<p>If Purchase (Debit) was mistakenly Credited, what to do in the correction?</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi  Board - 2015",
        "type": "board",
