        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>To fix a side flip, you must Debit the correct account with double the original amount.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 823,
        "text": "<p>Machinery installation 5k included in Wages. Correcting entry?</p>",
        "meta": "Sylhethet  Board - 2015",
