        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>Moving 5k from Wages (Expense) to Machinery (Asset) causes Expenses to decrease.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 825,
        "text": "<p>Cash 10k, Accounts Receivable 8k, Rent 7k, Pur 15k (Debit total: 40k). Accounts Payable 12k, Capital 20k, Sales 12k (Credit total: 44k). Suspense?</p>",
