        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>International Accounting Standards Committee.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 873,
        "text": "<p>Stock cost 15.5L, Market 20L. Why was it recorded at 15.5L?</p>",
        "meta": "Jashore  Board - 2017",
