        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Conservatism tells us to pick the lower of cost or market value.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 874,
        "text": "<p>Which are professional accounting bodies?i. ICAB, ii. ICMAB, iii. AICPA</p>",
        "meta": "Jashore  Board - 2017",
