        "explanation": "<p>Money Measurement (\u0985\u09b0\u09cd\u09a5\u09c7\u09b0 \u09ae\u09be\u09aa\u0995\u09be\u09a0\u09bf)\u2014only things measurable in money are recorded.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 882,
        "text": "<p>Depreciation is charged on fixed assets mainly because of?</p>",
        "meta": "Sylhethet  Board - 2016",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Matching Principle",
            "Conservatism",
            "Full Disclosure",
            "Materiality"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>To Match the cost of the asset against the revenue it helps generate.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 883,
        "text": "<p>The \"Trial Balance\" helps fulfill which accounting goal?</p>",
        "meta": "Barishal  Board - 2016",
