        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>They are primarily based on the Time Period and Matching principles.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 896,
        "text": "<p>Capital provided by the owner is a\u2014</p>",
        "meta": "Sylhethet  Board - 2015",
        "type": "board",
