    },
    {
        "id": 897,
        "text": "<p>Why is Capital a liability to the business?</p>",
        "meta": "Dhaka  Board - 2015",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Conservatism",
            "Going Concern",
            "Entity Concept",
            "Cost Principle"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>Entity Concept (\u09b8\u09cd\u09ac\u09a4\u09cd\u09ac\u09a8\u09c0\u09a4\u09bf) separates the owner from the business.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 898,
        "text": "<p>\"Every Debit must have an equal Credit\"\u2014which GAAP principle?</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi  Board - 2015",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Cost Principle",
            "Dual Aspect",
            "Realization",
            "Consistency"
