    {
        "id": 1013,
        "text": "<p>Read the stimulus and answer the question:\nKader Traders' Sales Journal for the month of June 2014 is as follows:\nDate | Particulars | Invoice | Terms | Ledger Folio | Amount (TK)\nJune 05 | Mitali Store | 105 | 2/10, n/30 | | 15,000 TK\nJune 20 | Bony Traders | 110 | 3/15, n/60 | | 20,000 TK\nTotal | | | | | 35,000 TK\nTrade Discount 5% on both.\nQ. If Bony Traders pays the full amount on June 28, how much Cash Discount will they receive?</p><div class=\"overflow-x-auto my-4\"><table class=\"min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200 dark:divide-gray-700 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700\"><tr class=\"bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800\"><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Date</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Particulars</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Invoice</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Terms</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Ledger Folio</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Amount (TK)</th></tr><tr class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-900\"><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">June 05</td><td c