            "8,235 TK",
            "5,310 TK"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>First, we find the balance of \"Good Debtors\" after adjusting for unrecorded sales and bad debt.Opening Accounts Receivable: 1,20,000 TK(+) Unrecorded Sales: 80,000 TK(-) New Bad Debt: 2,000 TK (17,000 TK - 15,000 TK)Balance: 1,98,000 TK2. Subtract New Bad Debt ProvisionBefore calculating a discount, you must subtract the bad debt provision (10%).Balance: 1,98,000 TK(-) New Provision (10%): 19,800 TKNet \"Good\" Debtors: 1,78,200 TK3. Calculate 5% DiscountApply the 5% rate to the remaining 1,78,200.1 TK,78,200 TK \\times 5\\% = \\mathbf{8,910 TK}TK</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1014,
        "text": "<p>Read the stimulus and answer the question:\nKader Traders' Sales Journal for the month of June 2014 is as follows:\nDate | Particulars | Invoice | Terms | Ledger Folio | Amount (TK)\nJune 05 | Mitali Store | 105 | 2/10, n/30 | | 15,000 TK\nJune 20 | Bony Traders | 110 | 3/15, n/60 | | 20,000 TK\nTotal | | | | | 35,000 TK\nTrade Discount 5% on both.\nQ. What will be the final balance of the Sales Account at the end of the month?</p><div class=\"overflow-x-auto my-4\"><table class=\"min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200 dark:divide-gray-700 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700\"><tr class=\"bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800\"><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Date</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Particulars</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Invoice</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Terms</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Ledger Folio</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Amount (TK)</th></tr><tr class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-900\"><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">June 05</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Mitali Store</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-right text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">105</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-right text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">2/10, n/30</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\"></td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-right text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">15,000 TK</td></tr><tr class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-900\"><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">June 20</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Bony Traders</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-right text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">110</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-right text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">3/15, n/60</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\"></td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-right text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">20,000 TK</td></tr><tr class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-900\"><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Total</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\"></td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\"></td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\"></td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\"></td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-right text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">35,000 TK</td></tr></table></div>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi  Board - 2017",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "39,000 TK",
            "36,800 TK",
            "32,000 TK",
            "24,800 TK"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>Total Bad Debt Expense = (Total Bad Debt + New Provision) - Old ProvisionTotal Bad Debt: 17,000 TK (from the adjustment).New Provision: 19,800 TK (calculated as 10% of the adjusted Accounts Receivable: 1,20,000 TK + 80,000 TK - 2,000 TK).Old Provision: 12,000 TK (from the Trial Balance credit side).Calculation:TK(17,000 TK + 19,800 TK) - 12,000 TK = \\mathbf{24,800 TK}TK</p>"
    },
