            "May 3"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Three months from Jan 31 (Feb, Mar, Apr). Since April has 30 days, the date is April 30.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1026,
        "text": "<p>Which is a \"Trade Receivable\"?</p>",
        "meta": "Chittagong - 2016",
