            "Debit Accounts Receivable / Credit Sales",
            "Debit Cash / Credit Accounts Receivable"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Debit: Bad Debt Expense / Credit: Provision for Bad Debt.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1029,
        "text": "<p>Who pays the \"Noting Charge\" if a bill is dishonored?</p>",
        "meta": "Dinajpur  Board - 2016",
