        "explanation": "<p>Though the drawer pays it initially, the Drawee (\u09a6\u09c7\u09a8\u09be\u09b0\u09c0) is ultimately responsible for the cost.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1030,
        "text": "<p>What is the main source of Accounts Receivable?</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi  Board - 2016",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Credit Sales",
            "Purchase",
            "Bad Debt",
            "Rent"
