        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>The worksheet is an optional working paper used to simplify the preparation of final accounts.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1155,
        "text": "<p>When prepaid rent expires, what is credited in the adjusting entry?</p>",
        "meta": "Dinajpur  Board - 2023",
        "type": "board",
