            "Accrued Interest. Debit; Interest. Credit",
            "Interest. Debit; Cash Credit",
            "P&Liability Debit; Interest. Credit"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>To reverse the adjustment from the previous year, we debit the liability and credit the expense.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1159,
        "text": "<p>What is the purpose of preparing closing entries?</p>",
        "meta": "Mymensingh - 2023",
