        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Closing entries reset the balances of temporary (nominal) accounts so the next period starts fresh.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1160,
        "text": "<p>Asset worksheet is usually prepared\u2014</p>",
        "meta": "Jashore  Board - 2022",
