        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>Subtracting both Cost of Goods Sold and operating expenses from sales yields the Operating Profit.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1286,
        "text": "<p>Stat in Trial Balance 1,000 TK. Opening Stock includes 150 stat; Closing includes 350 stat. Stationery used?</p>",
