        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Identifying an unused asset reduces the year's expense (iii) and keeps assets correct. It does not inflate stock if categorized separately.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1288,
        "text": "<p>Which of the following is an Intangible Asset?</p>",
        "meta": "Sylhethet  Board - 2025",
