        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Goodwill (\u09b8\u09c1\u09a8\u09be\u09ae) is an intangible asset as it has value but no physical substance.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1289,
        "text": "<p>Rent paid 12,000 TK (2/3 portion). How much is Rent Payable?</p>",
