    {
        "id": 1296,
        "text": "<p>Read the following stimulus and answer the question:\nTrial Balance (Partial)\nParticulars | Debit (TK) | Credit (TK)\nService Revenue | | 1,40,000 TK\nUnearned Revenue | | 60,000 TK\nAdjustment: Service Revenue of 20,000 TK has not been recorded.\nQ. If 3/4 portion of Unearned Service Revenue is earned, how much will be shown as Unearned Service Revenue in the Statement of Financial Position?</p><div class=\"overflow-x-auto my-4\"><table class=\"min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200 dark:divide-gray-700 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700\"><tr class=\"bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800\"><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Particulars</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Debit (TK)</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Credit (TK)</th></tr><tr class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-900\"><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Service Revenue</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\"></td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-right text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">1,40,000 TK</td></tr><tr class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-900\"><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Unearned Revenue</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\"></td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-right text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">60,000 TK</td></tr></table></div>",
