        "options": [
            "Copyright",
            "Goodwill",
            "Leasehold",
            "Disc. on Share"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>Discount on shares has no real value and is a fictitious asset. Others are intangible/fixed assets.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1468,
        "text": "<p>What type of asset is 'Goodwill'?</p>",
        "meta": "Dhaka  Board - 2021",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Investment",
            "Current Asset",
            "Fictitious Asset",
            "Intangible Asset"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>Goodwill is an asset that lacks physical substance but has long-term value.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1469,
        "text": "<p>Which of the following is a Fictitious Asset?</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi  Board - 2021",
