        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>Share discount (\u09b6\u09c7\u09af\u09bc\u09be\u09b0 \u09ac\u09be\u099f\u09cd\u099f\u09be) is a classic example of an \"Alik\" or fictitious asset.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1470,
        "text": "<p>Net Sales 3 TKLTK. Profit is 20 TK\\%TK on Cost of Goods Sold. What is the Cost of Goods Sold?</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi  Board - 2021",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "2,40,000 TK",
