            "3,60,000 TK"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>If Cost of Goods Sold is 100 TK\\%TK, Sales is 120 TK\\%TK. 3,00,000 TK / 1.2 = 2,50,000 TK</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1471,
        "text": "<p>From Q219: Indirect Expense is 30 TK\\%TK of Gross Profit. What is the Net Profit?</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi  Board - 2021",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "60,000 TK",
            "50,000 TK",
            "35,000 TK",
            "15,000 TK"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>Gross Profit = 3 TKL - 2.5L = 50kTK. Indirect Expense = 50 TKk \\times 30\\% = 15kTK. NP = 50 TKk - 15k = 35,000 TK</p>"
    },
