        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>VAT-able amount = 2,87,000 TK - 7,000 TK = 2,80,000 TK. VAT = 2,80,000 TK \\times 15/115 = 36,522 TK</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1474,
        "text": "<p>Required to prepare Balance Sheet\u2014\n\ni. Assets\n\nii. Liabilities\n\niii. Capital</p>",
        "meta": "Cumilla  Board - 2021",
