    },
    {
        "id": 1485,
        "text": "<p>Contingent Liability is placed in the Balance Sheet\u2014</p>",
        "meta": "Sylhethet  Board - 2021",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Asset Side",
            "Asset Footnote",
            "Liability Side",
            "Liability Footnote"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>Potential liabilities are not recognized in the table but mentioned in footnotes (\u09a6\u09be\u09af\u09bc \u09aa\u09be\u09b0\u09cd\u09b6\u09cd\u09ac\u09c7 \u09ab\u09c1\u099f\u09a8\u09cb\u099f\u09c7).</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1486,
        "text": "<p>Closing. Stock 65 TKkTK incl. fire loss 7 TKkTK (80 TK\\%TK insured) and stationery 4 TKkTK. Actual Closing. Stock?</p>",
        "meta": "Sylhethet  Board - 2021",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "54,000 TK",
            "55,400 TK",
            "68,000 TK",
            "76,000 TK"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Closing. Stock = 65,000 TK - 7,000 TK - 4,000 TK = 54,000 TK</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1487,
        "text": "<p>From Q235: Impact on Income Statement? (Net Loss from Fire 20 TK\\%TK)</p>",
        "meta": "Sylhethet  Board - 2021",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Income \u2193 1,400 TK",
            "Income \u2191 2,600 TK",
            "Expense \u2193 2,600 TK",
            "Expense \u2191 1,400 TK"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>Fire loss (20 TK\\%TK) = 1,400 TK. It is an expense that increases (\u09ac\u09cd\u09af\u09df \u09ac\u09be\u09dc\u09ac\u09c7 \u09e7,\u09ea\u09e6\u09e6 TK \u099f\u09be\u0995\u09be).</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1488,
        "text": "<p>The reason for the decrease in business capital is\u2014</p>",
        "meta": "Sylhethet  Board - 2021",
