        "options": [
            "i & ii",
            "ii & iii",
            "i & iii",
            "i, ii & iii"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>It reduces profit (i), book value of receivables (ii), and owner's capital (iii).</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1491,
        "text": "<p>Pur 50 TKkTK, Ship 6 TKkTK, Import 10 TKkTK, Sales 1 TKLTK, Return 3 TKkTK, Closing. Stock 15 TKkTK. Net Purchase?</p>",
