            "47,000 TK",
            "56,000 TK",
            "60,000 TK",
            "63,000 TK"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Net Purchase = Purchase (50 TKkTK) - Return (3 TKkTK) = 47,000 TK</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1492,
        "text": "<p>Pur 50 TKkTK, Ship 6 TKkTK, Import 10 TKkTK, Sales 1 TKLTK, Return 3 TKkTK, Closing. Stock 15 TKkTK. Gross Profit?</p>",
        "meta": "Barishal  Board - 2021",
        "type": "board",
