        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Net Pur = 47 TKkTK. Cost of Goods Sold = 47 TKk + 6k + 10k - 15k = 48,000 TK. Gross Profit = 1,00,000 TK - 48,000 TK = 52,000 TK</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1493,
        "text": "<p>What is 'Interest on Capital' for a business?</p>",
        "meta": "Barishal  Board - 2021",
