        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>It is a financial expense paid by the business to the owner for using their capital.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1494,
        "text": "<p>Cost of Goods Sold 40,000 TK. Profit is 25 TK\\%TK on Cost. Sales price?</p>",
