        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>Sales = Cost + Profit = 40,000 TK + (40,000 TK \\times 25\\%) = 50,000 TK</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1495,
        "text": "<p>Which of the following is a Current Liability?</p>",
