        "explanation": "<p>Unearned income (\u0985\u0997\u09cd\u09b0\u09bf\u09ae \u0986\u09df) represents an obligation to serve, making it a current liability.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1496,
        "text": "<p>Trial Balance Wages 18 TKkTK, Accrued 4 TKkTK. Incl. installation wages 2 TKkTK. Actual wage expense?</p>",
