        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Conservative principle: value at lower (20 TKkTK). Cost of Goods Sold increases by 10 TKkTK, so Gross Profit decreases by 10,000 TK</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1502,
        "text": "<p>Cost of Goods Sold 2.5 TKLTK, Opening. Expense 1 TKLTK, Apprentice Prem 30 TKkTK, Interest. on Capital 20 TKkTK. If Gross Profit is 1.5 TKLTK, Sales?</p>",
