        ],
        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>Sales = Cost of Goods Sold + Gross Profit = 2,50,000 TK + 1,50,000 TK = 4,00,000 TK</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1503,
        "text": "<p>From Q251: If Gross Profit is 2 TKLTK, what is the Net Profit?</p>",
        "meta": "Dinajpur  Board - 2021",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "50,000 TK",
