        ],
        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>NP = 2 TKLTK (Gross Profit) - 1 TKLTK (Opening Expense) + 30 TKkTK (Non-Opening Income) - 20 TKkTK (Non-Opening Expense) = 1,10,000 TK</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1504,
        "text": "<p>Non-operating expenses are\u2014\n\ni. Insurance\n\nii. Interest. on Loan\n\niii. Bank Charge</p>",
