        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Insurance is an operating expense. Loan interest and bank charges are financial (non-operating) expenses.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1505,
        "text": "<p>Paid Rent (2 TK/3 TK portion) 8,00,000 TK. Amount of Accrued Rent?</p>",
