    },
    {
        "id": 1512,
        "text": "<p>Net Sales 12 TKLTK, Cost of Goods Sold 7.5 TKLTK, Operating Expense (20% of Sales) + 10 TKkTK, Non-operating Income 20 TKkTK. Net Profit?</p>",
