    },
    {
        "id": 1518,
        "text": "<p>Prepaid Insurance 2 TKkTK. If it expires, what's the impact on Financial Statements?\n\ni. Prepaid \u2193\n\nii. Current Asset \u2193\n\niii. Ins. Expense \u2193</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi  Board - 2019",
