            "Insurance",
            "Travel Expense",
            "Purchase Discount",
            "Carriage Inward"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>Carriage Inward (Purchase Transportation) is a direct expense added to the cost of purchases.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1540,
        "text": "<p>Opening. Stock 33.5 TKkTK, Pur 60 TKkTK, Return 3 TKkTK, Disc 2 TKkTK. What is Net Purchase?</p>",
        "meta": "Cumillabined  Board - 2018",
