            "98,500 TK"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>Net Pur = Purchase (60 TKkTK) - Return (3 TKkTK) - Disc (2 TKkTK) = 55,000 TK</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1541,
        "text": "<p>Not included in Cost of Goods Sold\u2014\n\ni. Machine Carriage\n\nii. Office Expense\n\niii. Wage Expense</p>",
        "meta": "Cumillabined  Board - 2018",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "i & ii",
            "ii & iii",
            "i & iii",
            "i, ii & iii"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Machine carriage is capital Expense; Office Expense is indirect. Wages are direct (included).</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1542,
        "text": "<p>If profit is 20 TK\\%TK on Sales, what is the rate on Cost of Goods Sold?</p>",
        "meta": "Cumillabined  Board - 2018",
        "type": "board",
