            "20 TK\\%TK"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Formula: TKRate / (100 - Rate) = 20/80 = 25\\%TK.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1543,
        "text": "<p>Asset 5% commission must be paid on Net Profit before charging commission (Net Profit is 45,250 TK). Amount of commission?</p>",
        "meta": "Govt. Commerce College, Chattogram Board - 2018",
