        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>Paying a liability reduces Cash (Asset) and Accounts Payable (Liability); it does not affect Equity/Capital.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1548,
        "text": "<p>Which is NOT a component of Financial Statements?</p>",
