        "options": [
            "i & ii",
            "i & iii",
            "ii & iii",
            "i, ii, & iii"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>Capital is a BS item. Product drawing (Purchase \u2193) and Bad debt (Expense \u2191) are in IS.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1554,
        "text": "<p>Which is prepared using Capital items of a business?</p>",
        "meta": "Jashore  Board - 2017",
