        "explanation": "<p>The Balance Sheet (\u0986\u09b0\u09cd\u09a5\u09bf\u0995 \u0985\u09ac\u09b8\u09cd\u09a5\u09be\u09b0 \u09ac\u09bf\u09ac\u09b0\u09a3\u09c0) reflects assets, liabilities, and equity at a point in time.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1561,
        "text": "<p>Opening. Stock 15 TKkTK, Pur 1 TKLTK, Return 7.5 TKkTK, Disc 2.5 TKkTK, Wages 3 TKkTK, Duty 12 TKkTK, Closing. Stock 25 TKkTK. Cost of Goods Sold?</p>",
