        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>Net Pur = 90 TKkTK. Cost of Goods Sold = 15 TKk + 90k + 3k + 12k - 25k = 95,000 TK</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1562,
        "text": "<p>From Q306: Profit is 20 TK\\%TK on Sales. Gross Profit?</p>",
        "meta": "Barishal  Board - 2017",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "20,000 TK",
