        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>20 TK\\%TK on Sales = 25 TK\\%TK on Cost. Gross Profit = 95,000 TK \\times 25\\% = 23,750 TK</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1563,
        "text": "<p>Which of the following is an Internal Liability?</p>",
