        "explanation": "<p>Capital (\u09ae\u09c2\u09b2\u09a7\u09a8) is a liability of the business toward the owner.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1564,
        "text": "<p>Jan 1, 2015: Assets 2.2 TKLTK, Liability 90 TKkTK. Dec 31, 2015: Assets 2.7 TKLTK, Liability 1 TKLTK. Opening. Capital?</p>",
        "meta": "Dinajpur  Board - 2017",
