        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>Opening. Capital = Opening. Assets - Opening. Liability = 2,20,000 TK - 90,000 TK = 1,30,000 TK</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1565,
        "text": "<p>From Q309: Profit for the year 2015?</p>",
