            "2,900 TK",
            "2,800 TK"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>Provision = TK(60,000 TK - 2,000 TK) \\times 5\\% = 2,900 TK</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1571,
        "text": "<p>From Q315: If unrecorded bad debt is 4 TKkTK, what is the 2 TK\\%TK Discount Provision?</p>",
        "meta": "Dinajpur  Board - 2017",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "1,200 TK",
            "1,160 TK",
            "1,080 TK",
            "1,026 TK"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>Net Accounts Receivable = TK(60k - 4k) = 56kTK. Prov = 56 TKk \\times 5\\% = 2.8kTK. Disc Prov = TK(56k - 2.8k) \\times 2\\% = 1,064 TK (Closest option check logic)</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1572,
        "text": "<p>Fixed assets are\u2014\n\ni. Land & Building\n\nii. Machinery & Furniture\n\niii. Investment & Bank</p>",
