    },
    {
        "id": 1573,
        "text": "<p>Which of the following is NOT a Liquid Asset?</p>",
        "meta": "Dinajpur  Board - 2017",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Stock",
            "Receivables",
            "Cash",
            "Prepaid Insurance"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Liquid Assets = Current Assets - (Stock + Prepaid Expense). So, Stock/Inventory is not liquid.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1574,
        "text": "<p>What type of asset is Accounts Receivable?</p>",
