        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Accounts Receivable is a Current Asset as it represents money owed to the business that will be collected shortly.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1575,
        "text": "<p>Which of the following is a Fictitious (Dummy) Asset?</p>",
