            "1,50,000 TK",
            "1,52,000 TK",
            "1,53,000 TK",
            "1,55,000 TK"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Net Purchase = Purchase (1,55,000 TK) - Return (3,000 TK) - Discount (2,000 TK) = 1,50,000 TK.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1605,
        "text": "<p>Based on the data above, which costs will NOT be included in the Cost of Goods Sold?\n\ni. Machine Carriage\n\nii. Import Duty on Machine\n\niii. Wages & Salary</p>",
