            "i & iii",
            "ii & iii",
            "i, ii, & iii"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Carriage and Import Duty for a Machine are capital expenditures added to the asset cost, not Cost of Goods Sold. Wages & Salary is a revenue expense included in Cost of Goods Sold.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1606,
        "text": "<p>Which one is a Tangible Asset?</p>",
