            "37,500 TK",
            "52,500 TK"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>Total Ad = 50,000 TK + 20,000 TK = 70,000 TK. Deferred portion = 70,000 TK \\times \\frac{3}{4} = 52,500 TK.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1613,
        "text": "<p>Ad expense was TK 50,000 TK. Free product distribution TK 20,000 TK is unrecorded. If 1/4 of total ad expense is deferred, what is the amount of Deferred Advertisement?</p>",
