        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Total Ad = 50,000 TK + 20,000 TK = 70,000 TK. Deferred portion = 70,000 TK \\times \\frac{1}{4} = 17,500 TK.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1614,
        "text": "<p>Swadhin Traders: Capital 5,00,000 TK; 12% Loan 1,00,000 TK; Accrued Loan Interest 12,000 TK; Accounts Payable 40,000 TK; Advance Rent Received 40,000 TK; Fixed Assets 3,00,000 TK. What is the amount of Current Liabilities?</p>",
        "meta": "Cumilla Board - 2016",
