        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Current Liabilities = Accrued Interest (12,000 TK) + Accounts Payable (40,000 TK) + Advance Rent (40,000 TK) = 92,000 TK.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1615,
        "text": "<p>(Referring to the stem above) What is the total amount of Assets at the end of the year?</p>",
