        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>Total Assets = Total Liabilities + Capital = TK(1,00,000 TK + 92,000 TK) + 5,00,000 TK = 6,92,000 TK.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1616,
        "text": "<p>If Output VAT (received) is more than Input VAT (paid), where should the difference be shown?</p>",
