        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>Discount received is operating (related to purchases). Premium and Sub-let rent are non-operating.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1682,
        "text": "<p>Components of Financial Statements\u2014\n\ni. IS\n\nii. Cash Flow\n\niii. OE Statement</p>",
        "meta": "Ideal School",
        "type": "college",
        "options": [
            "i & ii",
            "i & iii",
            "ii & iii",
