    {
        "id": 1757,
        "text": "<p>Mrs. Tanisha has Opening. Capital: 50,000 TK and Closing. Capital: 75,000 TK. If she provides 10,000 TK as Additional Capital, what is the impact?\n\ni. Net profit will decrease by 10,000 TK\n\nii. Closing. Capital remains 75,000 TK in the Stmt of Affairs\n\niii. Closing. Capital increases by 10,000 TK</p>",
        "meta": "Dhaka Board - 2015",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "i & ii",
            "i & iii",
            "ii & iii",
            "i, ii & iii"
