        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Additional capital is deducted when calculating profit, so profit decreases. The closing balance of assets/liabilities (Closing. Capital) doesn't change unless the transaction happened on the closing date.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1758,
        "text": "<p>Which of the following is prepared to know the financial position in the Single Entry System?</p>",
