        "explanation": "<p>It is unscientific because it doesn't follow the duality principle of every transaction.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1762,
        "text": "<p>Single entry is popular where:\n\ni. Capital is low\n\nii. Transaction volume is low\n\niii. Complexity is low</p>",
        "meta": "Govt. Azizul Haque College",
