            "i, ii & iii"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>It is suitable for small-scale operations with simple transactions.</p>"
    },
    {
        "id": 1763,
        "text": "<p>What type of accounting method is Single Entry?</p>",
        "meta": "Jessore Govt. Mohila College",
        "type": "college",
        "options": [
            "Universally recognized",
            "Universally accepted",
            "Unscientific",
            "Scientific"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>It is not recognized by standard accounting bodies due to its incompleteness.</p>"
