        explanation: "<div class='text-xs space-y-1'><p>Rate = 20%. </p><p>Yr 1 Dep = 1,20,000. BV = 4,80,000.</p><p>Yr 2 Dep = 4,80,000 × 20% = <strong>96,000 Taka</strong>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
        id: 36,
        text: "<p>Read the following stem and answer the question:</p><p class='italic my-2 border-l-4 border-sky-400 pl-3 bg-sky-50 dark:bg-sky-900/10 py-2 text-[13px]'>Oronyo Ltd. purchased a machine on January 1, 2020, for 2,00,000 Taka. Reducing balance depreciation is charged at 20% annually.</p><p>Q. What amount will be shown for the machine in the Balance Sheet on Dec 31, 2021?</p>",
        meta: "Barisal Board · 2024",
