        text: "<p>Read the following stem and answer the question:</p><p class='italic my-2 border-l-4 border-sky-400 pl-3 bg-sky-50 dark:bg-sky-900/10 py-2 text-[13px]'>Oronyo Ltd. machine BV was 1,28,000 on Dec 31, 2021. It was sold for 1,00,000 on Dec 31, 2022. Rate is 20%.</p><p>Q. What is the amount of profit or loss on the sale?</p>",
        meta: "Barisal Board · 2024",
