    },
    {
        id: 38,
        text: "<p>If depreciation is over-charged-</p><p class='ml-4 my-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400'>i. It will decrease net income<br>ii. It will decrease owner's equity<br>iii. It will increase liabilities</p><p>Which of the following is correct?</p>",
