        id: 50,
        text: "<p>Read the following stem and answer the question:</p><p class='italic my-2 border-l-4 border-sky-400 pl-3 bg-sky-50 dark:bg-sky-900/10 py-2 text-[13px]'>Mr. Rupam purchased a machine on Jan 1, 2022, for 1,35,000 Taka. Installation cost was 25,000 Taka. Life is 5 years, salvage value is 10,000 Taka.</p><p>Q. What is the depreciable value of the machine?</p>",
