{
        id: 51,
        text: "<p>Read the following stem and answer the question:</p><p class='italic my-2 border-l-4 border-sky-400 pl-3 bg-sky-50 dark:bg-sky-900/10 py-2'>Mr. Rupam purchased a machine for 1,35,000 Taka on Jan 1, 2022. Installation cost was 25,000 Taka. Life is 5 years, salvage value is 10,000 Taka.</p><p>Q. What is the annual depreciation under the straight-line method?</p>",
