    },
    {
        id: 52,
        text: "<p>Depreciation affects-</p><p class='ml-4 my-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400'>i. Comprehensive Income Statement<br>ii. Statement of Changes in Equity<br>iii. Statement of Financial Position (Balance Sheet)</p><p>Which of the following is correct?</p>",
        meta: "Dhaka Board · 2023",
        type: "board",
        options: ["i & ii", "i & iii", "ii & iii", "i, ii & iii"],
        correctAnswer: 3,
        explanation: "<p>Depreciation is an expense (Income Statement), reduces net profit (Equity), and accumulates as a contra-asset (Balance Sheet).</p>"
    },
    {
        id: 53,
        text: "<p>Read the following stem and answer the question:</p><p class='italic my-2 border-l-4 border-sky-400 pl-3 bg-sky-50 dark:bg-sky-900/10 py-2 text-[13px]'>Mrs. Sharmin purchased a machine for 4,00,000 Taka on Jan 1, 2022. Carriage 5,000 Taka, installation 15,000 Taka. Life is 10 years, salvage value is 10,000 Taka.</p><p>Q. What is the depreciable value of the machine?</p>",
