        text: "<p>Read the following stem and answer the question:</p><p class='italic my-2 border-l-4 border-sky-400 pl-3 bg-sky-50 dark:bg-sky-900/10 py-2 text-[13px]'>Mrs. Sharmin machine's depreciable value is 4,10,000. Life is 10 years. Straight-line method is used.</p><p>Q. What is the accumulated depreciation at the end of 2024?</p>",
