        text: "<p>Read the following stem and answer the question:</p><p class='italic my-2 border-l-4 border-sky-400 pl-3 bg-sky-50 dark:bg-sky-900/10 py-2 text-[13px]'>Sumon Traders purchased a motor car for 80,000 Taka. Current accumulated depreciation is 48,000. The car is sold for 40,000 Taka.</p><p>Q. What is the profit or loss on the sale?</p>",
        meta: "Dinajpur Board · 2023",
        type: "board",
        options: ["Profit 8,000 Taka", "Loss 8,000 Taka", "32,000 Taka", "Loss 40,000 Taka"],
        correctAnswer: 0,
        explanation: "<p>Book Value = 80,000 - 48,000 = 32,000. Profit = 40,000 - 32,000 = <strong>8,000 Taka (Profit)</strong>.</p>"
    },
    {
        id: 73,
        text: "<p>Read the following stem and answer the question:</p><p class='italic my-2 border-l-4 border-sky-400 pl-3 bg-sky-50 dark:bg-sky-900/10 py-2 text-[13px]'>Sumon Traders sold a car (BV: 32,000) for 40,000 Taka, making an 8,000 profit.</p><p>Q. What is the impact on the accounting equation from this sale?</p>",
        meta: "Dinajpur Board · 2023",
