        options: ["i & ii", "i & iii", "ii & iii", "i, ii & iii"],
        correctAnswer: 2,
        explanation: "<p>The sale results in a net asset increase (Cash 40k in vs. Car 32k out) and an increase in Owner's Equity (8k profit). ii and iii are correct.</p>"
    },
    {
        id: 74,
        text: "<p>A machine cost 1,00,000 Taka. Installation was 40,000 Taka and salvage value 20,000 Taka. What is the second-year depreciation at 20% reducing balance?</p>",
