        correctAnswer: 1,
        explanation: "<div class='text-xs space-y-1'><p>Cost = 1,40,000. Yr 1 Dep = 28,000. </p><p>Yr 2 Dep = (1,40,000 - 28,000) × 20% = <strong>22,400 Taka</strong>.</p></div>"
    },
