        text: "<p>Read the following stem and answer the question:</p><p class='italic my-2 border-l-4 border-sky-400 pl-3 bg-sky-50 dark:bg-sky-900/10 py-2'>Muntasir Co. purchased a machine for 1,00,000 Taka on Jan 1, 2020. Life is 10 years, salvage value is 5,000 Taka.</p><p>Q. What is the reducing balance depreciation rate?</p>",
        meta: "Jessore Board · 2022",
