        text: "<p>Read the following stem and answer the question:</p><p class='italic my-2 border-l-4 border-sky-400 pl-3 bg-sky-50 dark:bg-sky-900/10 py-2 text-[13px]'>Machine cost 1,00,000. Rate 20% reducing balance.</p><p>Q. What is the second-year depreciation amount?</p>",
