        text: "<p>Read the following stem and answer the question:</p><p class='italic my-2 border-l-4 border-sky-400 pl-3 bg-sky-50 dark:bg-sky-900/10 py-2 text-[13px]'>Total Cost = 2,20,000. Life is 10 years. Reducing balance rate is 20%.</p><p>Q. What is the depreciation for the first two years?</p>",
