    {
        id: 84,
        text: "<p>Straight-line depreciation considers-</p><p class='ml-4 my-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400'>i. Purchase price<br>ii. Sales price<br>iii. Estimated life</p><p>Which of the following is correct?</p>",
