    },
    {
        id: 95,
        text: "<p>Read the following stem and answer the question:</p><p class='italic my-2 border-l-4 border-sky-400 pl-3 bg-sky-50 dark:bg-sky-900/10 py-2 text-[13px]'>Machine life is 5 years. Double reducing balance method is used.</p><p>Q. What will be the depreciation rate?</p>",
