{
        id: 101,
        text: "<p>Read the following stem and answer the question:</p><p class='italic my-2 border-l-4 border-sky-400 pl-3 bg-sky-50 dark:bg-sky-900/10 py-2'>Mr. Karim imported a machine for 10,00,000 Taka, paid 1,00,000 duty/dock charges, and 50,000 Taka transit insurance. He also spent 1,00,000 for installation.</p><p>Q. What type of expenditure is this insurance cost?</p>",
