        text: "<p>Read the following stem and answer the question:</p><p class='italic my-2 border-l-4 border-sky-400 pl-3 bg-sky-50 dark:bg-sky-900/10 py-2 text-[13px]'>Machine cost 4,00,000, installation 20,000. Life 10 yrs, salvage 1,00,000. 20% Reducing Balance used.</p><p>Q. What is the book value at the <strong>start</strong> of the second year?</p>",
