        id: 3,
        stem: "<p>Khan Ltd. imported a machine for 30,00,000 on July 1, 2023. Duty: 3,00,000; Carriage: 1,00,000; Installation: 2,00,000. Life 10 yrs, Salvage: 6,00,000. Reducing Balance method is used.</p>",
