        id: 12,
        stem: "<p>On Jan 1, 2020, Dihan Ent. bought a machine for 5,00,000. Costs incurred: Carriage 25,000, Expert fee 20,000, and Installation 15,000. Life 8 years, salvage 45,000. RB Method is used. Year ends Dec 31.</p>",
