                answer: "<div class='space-y-4 text-[10px]'><p class='font-bold underline text-center'>Accumulated Depreciation Ledger (Moving Balance)</p><table class='w-full border border-blue-300 shadow-md'><thead><tr class='bg-blue-50'><th class='border p-1'>Date</th> <th class='border p-1'>Description</th> <th class='border p-1'>Ref</th> <th class='border p-1'>Credit (Tk)</th> <th class='border p-1'>Balance (Tk)</th> </tr></thead><tbody><tr> <td class='border p-1'>2020 Dec 31</td> <td class='border p-1'>Depreciation Expense</td> <td class='border p-1'></td> <td class='border p-1 text-right'>1,30,000</td> <td class='border p-1 text-right'>1,30,000 (Cr)</td> </tr><tr> <td class='border p-1'>2021 Dec 31</td> <td class='border p-1'>Depreciation Expense</td> <td class='border p-1'></td> <td class='border p-1 text-right'>1,04,000</td> <td class='border p-1 text-right'>2,34,000 (Cr)</td> </tr><tr> <td class='border p-1'>2022 Dec 31</td> <td class='border p-1'>Depreciation Expense</td> <td class='border p-1'></td> <td class='border p-1 text-right'>83,200</td> <td class='border p-1 text-right'>3,17,200 (Cr)</td> </tr><tr> <td class='border p-1'>2023 Dec 31</td> <td class='border p-1'>Depreciation Expense</td> <td class='border p-1'></td> <td class='border p-1 text-right font-bold'>66,560</td> <td class='border p-1 text-right font-bold bg-blue-100/50'>3,83,760 (Cr)</td> </tr></tbody></table></div>"
