        "id": 3562
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: Fast Ltd. has purchased a machine for business expansion. By using the machine, the company will be able to achieve the ultimate goal of finance by increasing production and sales.\n\n\n\nQ: Which function of finance has Fast Ltd. performed?</p>",
        "meta": "Chittagong Board · 2025",
