        "id": 3563
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: (Same as above)\n\n\n\nQ: The advantages of the goal of finance that Fast Ltd. is expected to achieve are:\n\n\ni. Considering cash flows\n\n\nii. Considering time value of money\n\n\niii. Considering risk</p>",
