        "explanation": "<p>Spreading investments across different sectors minimizes overall risk.</p>",
        "id": 3566
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Reasons for a liquidity crisis: i. Excessive investment, ii. Excessive credit sales, iii. Debt repayment.</p>",
        "meta": "Barisal Board · 2025",
