        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>There is an inverse relationship; holding too much idle cash reduces potential investment returns.</p>",
        "id": 3575
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: Mr. Akhtar invests capital in a business with the expectation of making a profit, but fails to achieve the expected profit after a certain period. He reinvests in multiple projects with the expectation of higher profits.\n\n\n\nQ: What was the primary goal of Mr. Akhtar's business in the stem?</p>",
