        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Wealth maximization aims to increase share market value, linked to positive N<code>PV</code> projects.</p>",
        "id": 3579
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: Mr. Arif is a financial manager of a company. To invest in a profitable project, he takes a loan of TK 30 lakh from X Bank at 12% interest. At the end of the year, he earns a profit of TK 5 lakh from that project.\n\n\n\nQ: Which principle of finance did Mr. Arif follow?</p>",
        "meta": "Mymensingh Board · 2025",
        "type": "board",
