        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>He is balancing the high risk of debt against the expected high return of the project.</p>",
        "id": 3580
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: (Same as above)\n\n\n\nQ: The decisions taken by Mr. Arif are:\n\n\ni. Dividend decision\n\n\nii. Financing decision\n\n\niii. Investment decision</p>",
