        "id": 3602
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: 'P' Traders invested most of its capital in a single project. After some time, the organization faced a business crisis as it failed to pay the dues of its creditors.\n\n\n\nQ: Which principle of finance did 'P' Traders fail to follow?</p>",
        "meta": "Sylhet Board · 2025",
