            "Liquidity and Profit",
            "Portfolio",
            "Dividend payment"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>By tying up too much cash in a long-term project, they lacked the liquidity to pay short-term debts.</p>",
        "id": 3603
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: (Same as above)\n\n\n\nQ: What measure can 'P' Traders take to overcome the business crisis immediately?</p>",
        "meta": "Sylhet Board · 2025",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
