            "Issue Preferred Shares",
            "Long-term loan",
            "Short-term loan"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>A short-term loan provides the immediate cash (liquidity) needed to pay off urgent creditors.</p>",
        "id": 3604
    },
    {
