        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>The primary trade-offs in financial management are between risk vs. return and liquidity vs. profitability.</p>",
        "id": 3630
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>A firm's social responsibility includes: i. Providing fair wages, ii. Safe working environment, iii. Profit maximization. Which is correct?</p>",
        "meta": "Chittagong Board · 2023",
