    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: Mr. Ruhul is a small investor. He invested his capital in a poultry farm and apple-plum cultivation. Although many people suffered losses by investing in a single farm, he was able to make a profit.\n\n\n\nQ: Which investment principle has Mr. Ruhul adopted?</p>",
