        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Risk and Return",
            "Liquidity and Profit",
            "Cost Control",
            "Portfolio Diversification"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>Investing in two different types of agriculture/farming to spread risk is a Portfolio Diversification strategy.</p>",
        "id": 3639
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: (Same as above)\n\n\n\nQ: As a result of Mr. Ruhul's investment in multiple farms—\n\n\ni. Risk has decreased\n\n\nii. Profit was higher\n\n\niii. Farm planning has become easier</p>",
        "meta": "Sylhet Board · 2023",
