        "options": [
            "i & ii",
            "i & iii",
            "ii & iii",
            "i, ii & iii"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Diversification reduces risk and can lead to more stable/higher profits, though it usually makes planning more complex.</p>",
        "id": 3640
    },
    {
