        "options": [
            "Social welfare",
            "Earning profit",
            "Business success",
            "Correct use of assets"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Governments manage finance primarily to maximize the collective welfare of the society.</p>",
        "id": 3655
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What is it called when investment is made in multiple projects?</p>",
        "meta": "Mymensingh Board · 2023",
