        "options": [
            "Time value of money principle",
            "Liquidity principle",
            "Suitability principle",
            "Portfolio principle"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>The Portfolio Principle involves spreading capital across multiple assets to minimize risk.</p>",
        "id": 3656
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What happens if a business's debtors (Accounts Receivable) increase?</p>",
        "meta": "Mymensingh Board · 2023",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Cash inflow decreases",
            "Reputation increases",
            "Liability increases",
            "Asset increases"
