        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>Debtors/Accounts Receivable are current assets; an increase in them increases the total assets of the firm.</p>",
        "id": 3657
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Sources of public finance: i. Treasury Bill, ii. Income Tax, iii. Import Duty.</p>",
        "meta": "Mymensingh Board · 2023",
