        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>Governments collect corporate taxes and income taxes from profitable businesses and their employees.</p>",
        "id": 3678
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What is the relationship between risk and profit?</p>",
        "meta": "Comilla Board · 2022",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Positive",
            "Negative",
            "Neutral",
