    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: Mr. Showkat works in a private bank. Out of interest in the stock market, he purchased shares of Meghna Oil Ltd. with all his savings. Because Meghna Oil Ltd. is in a good position, it provides scholarships to brilliant students every year and plants trees on both sides of the road to prevent environmental pollution.\n\n\n\nQ: Which principle did Mr. Showkat fail to follow in his investment?</p>",
        "meta": "Sylhet Board · 2022",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Time value of money",
            "Business cycle principle",
