        ],
        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>They failed to balance liquidity with profit distribution, leaving no cash for operational needs (raw materials).</p>",
        "id": 3702
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: (Same as above)\n\n\n\nQ: The decisions taken by Nazrul Ltd. in the stem are related to:\n\n\ni. Financing\n\n\nii. Investment\n\n\niii. Dividend</p>",
