    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: Mr. Arif is the owner of a business. Last year he earned TK 1 crore. He kept TK 20 lakh as liquidity and deposited the remaining TK 80 lakh in the Post Office.\n\n\n\nQuestion: If Mr. Arif deposits his entire income in the Post Office, then—\n\n\ni. Profitability will increase\n\n\nii. Liquidity will decrease\n\n\niii. Probability of bankruptcy will increase</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi Board · 2021",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "i & ii",
            "i & iii",
            "ii & iii",
            "i, ii & iii"
