    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: Mr. Ariz is the financial manager of a large firm. He always tries to achieve a goal that emphasizes maximizing the gap between the firm's income and expenditure.\n\n\n\nQuestion: In the language of finance, what is the goal followed by Mr. Ariz called?</p>",
