        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>While sales matter, the financial objectives are focused on maximizing profit and, ultimately, the value/wealth of the firm.</p>",
        "id": 3765
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What is the main goal of public finance?</p>",
        "meta": "Barisal · 2021",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Profit maximization",
            "Business expansion",
            "Wealth increase",
            "Social welfare"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>(Repeat of 207) The government manages funds specifically for the collective good of society.</p>",
        "id": 3766
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Which is a major function of finance?</p>",
