        ],
        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Procurement (collection) of funds is the starting and primary functional role of finance.</p>",
        "id": 3767
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>If liquidity increases— i. Profit decreases, ii. Profit increases, iii. Cost decreases</p>",
        "meta": "Dinajpur · 2021",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "i, ii",
            "ii, iii",
            "i, iii",
            "i, ii, iii"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Keeping more idle cash (liquidity) means less money is being invested to earn a return, thus reducing profit.</p>",
        "id": 3768
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What is the purpose of portfolio investment?</p>",
        "meta": "Dinajpur · 2021",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Risk reduction",
            "Cost reduction",
            "Profit reduction",
            "Income reduction"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>By diversifying across multiple assets, the risk associated with any single asset's failure is minimized.</p>",
        "id": 3769
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What is the first consideration in public finance?</p>",
