        "explanation": "<p>Wealth maximization is superior to profit maximization because it considers the timing of cash flows (TVM), risk, and total cash flows.</p>",
        "id": 3772
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Financing activities include— i. Purchasing furniture, ii. Issuing shares, iii. Paying dividends</p>",
        "meta": "Dinajpur · 2021",
