        "explanation": "<p>Wealth maximization is the modern and ultimate goal of finance as it maximizes the market value of the company's shares.</p>",
        "id": 3776
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Functions of finance are— i. Fund distribution, ii. Fund collection, iii. Capital budgeting decision</p>",
        "meta": "Mymensingh · 2021",
