        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>These three represent the primary roles of a financial manager: sourcing, investing, and returning funds.</p>",
        "id": 3777
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What is the main goal of public finance?</p>",
        "meta": "Mymensingh · 2021",
