        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Public finance is managed by the state with the primary intent of ensuring the welfare and security of the public.</p>",
        "id": 3778
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What is the main purpose of forming a portfolio?</p>",
        "meta": "Mymensingh · 2021",
