        "explanation": "<p>Non-trading organizations (like NGOs or clubs) exist primarily to provide services to society, not to earn profit.</p>",
        "id": 3780
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: Mondal Ent. invested most funds in one project and failed to pay creditors. Q: Which principle was violated?</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi · 2019",
        "type": "board",
