            "Portfolio",
            "Suitability"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>By locking up all cash in a long-term project, they lacked the liquidity needed to pay short-term creditors.</p>",
        "id": 3781
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: (Same as above) Q: What is the immediate way to overcome this crisis?</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi · 2019",
