            "Take a short-term loan",
            "Issue rights shares"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>A short-term loan is the fastest way to resolve an immediate cash shortage or liquidity crisis.</p>",
        "id": 3782
    },
    {
