    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: (Same as above) Q: Advantages of Mr. Robin's goal include— i. Considering TVM, ii. Considering cash flows, iii. Considering risk</p>",
        "meta": "Dinajpur · 2019",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "i & ii",
            "i & iii",
            "ii & iii",
            "i, ii & iii"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>Wealth Maximization is considered superior because it accounts for the time value of money, risk, and cash flows.</p>",
        "id": 3796
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Which of the following is a function of business finance?</p>",
        "meta": "Dhaka · 2019",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Preparing Income Statement",
            "Preparing Balance Sheet",
            "Ensuring proper use of funds",
            "Production & distribution"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>Finance focuses on the procurement and the most efficient/profitable use of funds.</p>",
        "id": 3797
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Wealth maximization concept considers— i. Cash profit, ii. Time value of money, iii. All cash & non-cash flows</p>",
        "meta": "Dhaka · 2019",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "i & ii",
            "i & iii",
            "ii & iii",
            "i, ii & iii"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>It prioritizes net cash flows and their timing (TVM) rather than accounting profits or non-cash items.</p>",
        "id": 3798
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: BD Food Ltd. provides quality food at low cost and tries to maximize profit. Q: What is this effort called?</p>",
        "meta": "Combined · 2018",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Wealth maximization",
