        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>The stem explicitly mentions the goal of achieving the \"highest profit,\" which refers to profit maximization.</p>",
        "id": 3799
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: (Same as above) Q: The activities of BD Food Ltd.— i. Acts as a measure of efficiency, ii. Proper use of assets, iii. Social welfare is achieved</p>",
        "meta": "Combined · 2018",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "i & ii",
            "i & iii",
            "ii & iii",
            "i, ii & iii"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>Successful business operations indicate efficiency and resource management while providing quality goods serves society.</p>",
        "id": 3800
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Purchasing shares of multiple companies instead of just one follows which principle?</p>",
        "meta": "Dhaka · 2017",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Profit & Liquidity",
