        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>The core scope of finance involves the procurement (collection) and effective utilization (investment) of funds.</p>",
        "id": 3812
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Revenue income is related to which of the following?</p>",
        "meta": "- · -",
