        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>Wealth maximization is considered the superior objective as it focuses on increasing the market value of the firm's shares.</p>",
        "id": 3815
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What is the first consideration in family finance?</p>",
