        "text": "<p>Stem: Mr. X took a 7 Lakh bribe, embezzled 4 Lakh by manipulating accounts, and sent 5 Lakh abroad illegally.\n\nQ: Which incident falls under \"Embezzlement of Funds\"?</p>",
