        "meta": "Dhaka Commerce College · 2026",
        "type": "college"
    },
    {
        "id": "fin1-ch2-short-b-020",
        "text": "Who are the participants in the money market? Explain.",
        "answer": "1. Major participants include the Central Bank (Bangladesh Bank), commercial banks, and non-banking financial institutions.\n\n2. Large corporations and government agencies also participate to manage short-term cash surpluses or deficits.",
        "meta": "Dhaka Commerce College · 2026",
