    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: Mr. Rubel takes a loan of TK 2,000 at 5% interest.\n\nQ: Under compound interest, after 4 years—\n\ni. <code>FV</code> will be TK 2,431\n\nii. Interest will be TK 431\n\niii. Compound interest will be double of simple interest</p>",
