            "30,130",
            "29,130"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>$Interest = 50,000 \\times \\frac{270}{365} \\times 0.08 = 2,958.9$. Total $= 50,000 + 2,958 = 52,958.9$ (Option A is closest).</p>",
        "id": 4064
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: Mr. Zakir takes a TK 50,000 loan at 18% for 2 years, with monthly installments.\n\nQ: How many installments will he pay?</p>",
        "meta": "Ctg · 2022",
