            "34,977",
            "35,909"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Using <code>PV</code>A = A \\times [\\frac{1-(1+i)^{-n}}{i}]$:\n\n$50,000 = A \\times [\\frac{1-(1.015)^{-24}}{0.015}] \\rightarrow A = 2,496.2$.</p>",
        "id": 4066
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>For which compounding frequency will the Future Value be the lowest?</p>",
