        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>If the discount rate is lower, you don't need as much money today to reach a future goal.</p>",
        "id": 4074
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What is it called when interest is charged on Interest + Principal?</p>",
        "meta": "Barisal · 2022",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Compound Int.",
