        "id": 4078
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: (Same as above)\n\nQ: To make a decision, what should the landowner do?</p>",
        "meta": "Barisal · 2022",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Find PV of annual flows",
            "Find PV of annuity",
            "Find FV of lump sum",
            "Find FV of annuity"
        ],
