        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p><code>FV</code> represents the value at the end of the timeline, often called Terminal Value.</p>",
        "id": 4080
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What is the relationship between Time ($n$), Interest Rate ($i$), and Future Value (<code>FV</code>)?</p>",
        "meta": "Dinajpur · 2022",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Positive",
            "Negative",
            "Neutral",
            "Proportional"
