        "id": 4083
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: Mr. Karim wants to buy a laptop for TK 80,000 in 5 years. Shaluk Bank offers 8% annual interest. Chandra Bank offers 7% semi-annual interest.\n\nQ: How much to deposit now in Shaluk Bank?</p>",
