        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Investors focus on <code>PV</code> to decide if an investment's cost today is worth the future returns.</p>",
        "id": 4086
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>For semi-annual compounding, how many times will it compound in 2 years?</p>",
