        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>Discounting (বাট্টাকরণ) is the process of finding <code>PV</code>.</p>",
        "id": 4095
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>For quarterly compounding, what is the value of $m$?</p>",
