        "explanation": "<p>Rule 72 specifically estimates the doubling time of an investment.</p>",
        "id": 4097
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What is included in a Loan Amortization Schedule?\n\ni. Installment amount\n\nii. Interest amount\n\niii. Principal amount</p>",
