        "id": 4102
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>To repay a loan, each installment must consist of—\n\ni. Interest\n\nii. Principal\n\niii. Charges</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi · 2021",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
