        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Installments are split into principal and interest. Charges are separate costs.</p>",
        "id": 4103
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What is the method of determining Present Value called?</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi · 2021",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Compounding",
            "Discounting",
            "Growing",
            "Transferring"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Discounting (বাট্টাকরণ) finds the current value of future money.</p>",
        "id": 4104
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Annuity Due (অগ্রিম বার্ষিকী) is paid—\n\ni. End of year\n\nii. Beginning of year\n\niii. Start of the term</p>",
