        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>\"Beginning\" and \"Start\" mean the same thing for Annuity Due.</p>",
        "id": 4105
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: Mr. Ali deposits TK 1,00,000 in a scheme for 5 years at 10% compound interest.\n\nQ: What type of cash flow is his deposit?</p>",
