        "id": 4133
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>The Discounting Method is—\n\ni. Associated with Present Value.\nii. The opposite of Compounding.\niii. The process of determining the amount of Discount.</p>",
        "meta": "Ctg · 2021",
        "type": "board",
