            "i, ii & iii"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Consumption preference and risk are the core psychological drivers of TVM.</p>",
        "id": 4213
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Mr. Rafiq needs a 10 Lakh fund in 5 years. At 12% interest, how much to deposit today?</p>",
        "meta": "Dinajpur · 2016",
