        "explanation": "<p>Interest $= 5,000 \\times 5 \\times 0.12 = 3,000$. Total $= 5,000 + 3,000 = 8,000$.</p>",
        "id": 4227
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Mr. Jawad deposits TK 10,000 at 10% interest for 5 years. How much will he receive?</p>",
        "meta": "Ctg · 2015",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "15,000",
