        "id": 4228
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: Ms. Nijhum borrows TK 20,000 for 4 years at 8% annual compound interest.\n\nQ: What is the total Compound Interest amount?</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi · 2015",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "2,950",
