        "id": 4229
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: (Same as above)\n\nQ: If Ms. Nijhum took the loan at Simple Interest, what would the Future Value be?</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi · 2015",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "23,220",
            "24,355",
            "25,950",
            "26,400"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p><code>FV</code> = 20,000 + (20,000 \\times 4 \\times 0.08) = 26,400$.</p>",
        "id": 4230
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Stem: Mr. Arif invests TK 20,000 for 5 years at 12% semi-annual compounding.\n\nQ: How much will he receive after 5 years?</p>",
        "meta": "Sylhet · 2015",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "28,615",
