        "id": 4298
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Shapla Ltd produces juice. Fixed cost is 50,000, production cost is 10 per bottle, and selling price is 20. How many bottles to sell for zero profit/loss?</p>",
        "meta": "Barisal Board · 2017",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "500",
            "2,500",
            "5,000",
