        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Both B and D are current assets, but Accounts Receivable is the more conventional primary answer.</p>",
        "id": 4318
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Which is considered a current asset?</p>",
        "meta": "- · -",
