        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Under the indirect method, an increase in current assets (Debtors) is treated as a cash outflow (use of cash).</p>",
        "id": 4330
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Into how many activities is cash flow divided in a Cash Flow Statement?</p>",
