        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>Trade credit is usually granted without collateral, based on the buyer's creditworthiness.</p>",
        "id": 4430
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>For which of the following loans is a \"Compensating Balance\" required?</p>",
