    },
    {
        "id": "fin1-ch5-short-b-035",
        "text": "What problems arise from holding excessive inventory? Explain.",
        "answer": "Excessive inventory ties up working capital, increases storage and insurance costs, and risks loss through damage or obsolescence.",
        "meta": "Ispahani Public School, Comilla · 2026",
        "type": "college"
    },
    {
        "id": "fin1-ch5-short-a-036",
