            },
            {
                "label": "c",
                "text": "Calculate the EOQ for Shonchoi Company.",
                "answer": "1. Data: $A = 800 \\times 12 = 9,600; O = 100; C = 1$.\n\n2. Formula: $EOQ = \\sqrt{\\frac{2 \\times A \\times O}{C}}$.\n\n3. Calculation: $\\sqrt{\\frac{2 \\times 9,600 \\times 100}{1}} =$ 1,386 units."
