        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>$$YTM = \\frac{240 + (2000-1500)/10}{(2000+1500)/2} = \\frac{290}{1750} \\approx 16.57\\%$$.</p>",
        "id": 4492
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>From the company's perspective, positive aspects of bonds include: (i) Fixed cost (ii) Lower capital cost (iii) Tax benefits.</p>",
