        "id": 4588
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Mr. Tamim invested in a 5-year zero-coupon bond (<code>FV</code> 1,000) with a 10% expected return. What is its current value?</p>",
        "meta": "Jessore Board · 2022",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "621 TK",
            "900 TK",
            "909 TK",
            "1,000 TK"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p><code>PV</code> = 1000 / (1.10)^5 = 620.92 \\approx 621$ TK.</p>",
        "id": 4589
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What financial benefit will Mr. Tamim receive from his zero-coupon bond investment?</p>",
        "meta": "Jessore Board · 2022",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Capital Gain",
            "Coupon",
            "Yield",
            "Commission"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>The difference between the discounted purchase price and the face value is a capital gain.</p>",
        "id": 4590
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Long-term financing sources for a Joint Stock Co. include: (i) Debt capital (ii) Common shares (iii) Preferred shares.</p>",
        "meta": "Jessore Board · 2022",
        "type": "board",
