        ],
        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>All three are standard components of a company's long-term capital structure.</p>",
        "id": 4591
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Which securities are free from \"fixed costs\" (legally binding fixed payments)?</p>",
        "meta": "Comilla Board · 2022",
