        "id": 4593
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>If the required rate of return increases from 10% to 12%, what happens to the bond's intrinsic value?</p>",
        "meta": "Comilla Board · 2022",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Price will increase",
            "Price will decrease",
            "No change",
            "No relationship"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>There is an inverse relationship; as the required rate (discount rate) goes up, the present value goes down.</p>",
        "id": 4594
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What is the full form of IPO?</p>",
        "meta": "Comilla Board · 2022",
