            "Internal Public Offering",
            "Initial Public Offering",
            "International Public Offering"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>An IPO is the first sale of stock by a private company to the public.</p>",
        "id": 4595
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Which of the following is NOT an authority that issues bonds?</p>",
