        "id": 4596
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Characteristics of a Zero Coupon Bond include: (i) Sold at par (ii) Sold at discount (iii) No coupon rate.</p>",
        "meta": "Chittagong Board · 2022",
        "type": "board",
