        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Zero-coupon bonds are always sold at a discount (below par) and have a 0% coupon rate.</p>",
        "id": 4597
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>A bond has a 10% coupon, 1,000 face value, and 10-year maturity. What type of bond is this?</p>",
        "meta": "Chittagong Board · 2022",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "Treasury Bond",
            "Zero Coupon Bond",
            "Coupon Bond",
