        "id": 4711
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Based on the prompt (Jerin: Value 1761, Price 2000; Shakil: Value 900, Price 1000; Hasan: Value 1400, Price 1200), which is a good buy?</p>",
        "meta": "- · -",
