        "id": "fin1-ch7-cq-018",
        "stem": "The capital structure of Sony Company Limited is as follows:\n\n*table\n| Source of Capital | Amount (Taka) |\n| :--- | :--- |\n| Common Stock | 10,00,000 |\n| 10% Preferred Stock | 2,50,000 |\n| 14% Debenture | 7,50,000 |\n| **Total** | **20,00,000** |\n\nThe selling price of each common share is 50 Taka. The expected rate of return (dividend) this year is 4 Taka. The dividend growth rate is 5%. The company's tax rate is 40%.",
