        "type": "board",
        "questions": [
            {
                "label": "a",
                "text": "What is the cost of retained earnings?",
                "answer": "The cost of retained earnings is the opportunity cost associated with the earnings that a company keeps rather than distributing to shareholders as dividends. It represents the return shareholders could have earned if they had invested those dividends elsewhere."
