            {
                "label": "c",
                "text": "Calculate the cost of common stock for Magpie Ltd.",
                "answer": "Calculation for Cost of Common Stock ($K_e$):\n\nCurrent Dividend ($D_0$) = 2 Taka\n\nGrowth Rate ($g$) = 6% or 0.06\n\nMarket Price ($P_0$) = 150 Taka\n\nExpected Dividend ($D_1$) = $D_0(1+g) = 2(1+0.06) = 2.12$ Taka\n\nFormula:\n\n$K_e = (\\frac{D_1}{P_0} + g) \\times 100$\n\n$K_e = (\\frac{2.12}{150} + 0.06) \\times 100$\n\n$K_e = (0.01413 + 0.06) \\times 100 = 7.413\\%$\n\nAnswer: 7.41%"
            },
