    {
        "id": "fin1-ch7-cq-020",
        "stem": "The capital structure of 'United Leasing' company is as follows:\n\n*table\n| Source of Capital | Amount (Taka) |\n| :--- | :--- |\n| Common Stock | 5,00,000 |\n| 13% Preferred Stock | 2,00,000 |\n| 14% Debenture | 3,00,000 |",
