        "stem": "The capital structure of Mahdia and Cleopatra Joint Venture Ltd. is as follows:\n\n*table\n| Source of Capital | Amount (Taka) |\n| :--- | :--- |\n| Common Stock Capital (10 Taka each) | 5,00,000 |\n| 11% Preferred Stock Capital | 3,00,000 |\n| 14% Debt Capital | 4,00,000 |\n| **Total** | **12,00,000** |",
