    {
        "id": "fin1-ch7-cq-030",
        "stem": "The capital structure of Nishat Ltd. is as follows:\n\n*table\n| Source of Capital | Amount (Taka) |\n| :--- | :--- |\n| Common Stock Capital | 5,00,000 |\n| 8% Preferred Stock Capital | 2,00,000 |\n| 10% Bond | 3,00,000 |\n| **Total** | **10,00,000** |",
