        "options": [
            "Project Evaluation",
            "Implementation",
            "Project Identification",
            "Analysis"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>The process begins with identifying or generating new investment ideas/opportunities.</p>",
        "id": 4821
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>An independent project is generally accepted when:</p>",
