        "explanation": "<p><code>PV</code> \\text{ of Anuity} = 30,000 \\t\times 3.7908 = 1,13,724$$. $$NPV = 1,13,724 - 1,00,000 = 13,724 \\approx 13,730$.</p>",
        "id": 4825
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>To increase N<code>PV</code>, XYZ Co. should: (i) Decrease discount rate (ii) Increase cash inflows (iii) Decrease cash inflows.</p>",
        "meta": "Dinajpur Board · 2025",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "i & iii",
