        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>A shorter Payback Period (PBP) is preferred as it indicates faster recovery of capital.</p>",
        "id": 4827
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Required for Payback Period (PBP) calculation: (i) Cash inflows (ii) Discount rate (iii) Initial investment.</p>",
        "meta": "Dinajpur Board · 2025",
