        ],
        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Standard PBP ignores the discount rate; it only needs investment and annual cash flows.</p>",
        "id": 4828
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What should be added to Net Profit After Tax (<code>EAT</code>) to get Cash Flow After Tax (CFAT)?</p>",
