        "explanation": "<p>Its primary role is evaluating and selecting long-term assets or projects.</p>",
        "id": 4830
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Discounted Cash Flow (DCF) methods include: (i) N<code>PV</code> (ii) ARR (iii) <code>IRR</code>.</p>",
        "meta": "Mymensingh · 2025",
