        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "20,000",
            "22,000",
            "24,000",
            "25,000"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>$$Cost = 1,00,000 + 20,000 = 1,20,000$$. $$Dep = (1,20,000 - 10,000) / 5 = 22,000$$.</p>",
        "id": 4913
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Flora Co: Avg Profit = (22+20+15+10+17)/5 = 16.8k. Avg Inv = (120k+10k)/2 = 65k. ARR?</p>",
        "meta": "Dhaka Board · 2022",
