            "25.84%",
            "28.00%",
            "33.60%"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>$$ARR = (16,800 / 65,000) \\t\times 100 \\approx 25.84\\%$$.</p>",
        "id": 4914
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Most acceptable method for project evaluation?</p>",
        "meta": "Dhaka Board · 2022",
