        "explanation": "<p>Need 20k from Yr 4's 40k. $$PBP = 3 + (20,000/40,000) = 3.5$$ years.</p>",
        "id": 4920
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Project is acceptable because: (i) N<code>PV</code> is positive (ii) N<code>PV</code> is 22,500 (iii) TVM considered.</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi · 2022",
