        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>$$NPV = 1,02,500 - 1,00,000 = 2,500$$ (Not 22,500). So ii is wrong.</p>",
        "id": 4921
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Capital budgeting is applied for: (i) Asset replacement (ii) Liquidity (iii) Fixed asset purchase.</p>",
        "meta": "Jessore · 2022",
