        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>N<code>PV</code> and <code>IRR</code> are discounted methods; ARR ignores time value.</p>",
        "id": 4926
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Capital budgeting decision is what kind of process for a firm?</p>",
        "meta": "Jessore Board · 2022",
