        "id": 4931
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Advantages of Discounted Cash Flow (DCF) methods: (i) Considers TVM (ii) Considers Risk (iii) Considers Cash Flow.</p>",
        "meta": "Comilla Board · 2022",
