    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Limitations of the method used by Mrs. Borsha: (i) Ignores TVM (ii) Ignores cash inflows (iii) Dividing profit/investment by different numbers.</p>",
        "meta": "Mymensingh · 2022",
        "type": "board",
