        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>ARR's main flaw is ignoring the time value of money and using accounting profit.</p>",
        "id": 4974
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What is obtained after deducting all expenses including tax from sales?</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi · 2021",
