        "explanation": "<p>The final residual profit after all deductions is the Net Profit.</p>",
        "id": 4975
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Capital budgeting evaluation methods include: (i) ARR (ii) PBP (iii) N<code>PV</code>.</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi · 2021",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "i & ii",
