        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>All three are standard project evaluation techniques.</p>",
        "id": 4976
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Formula for Payback Period (PBP) with equal installments:</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi · 2021",
        "type": "board",
        "options": [
            "PBP=NCB/NCO",
            "PBP=NCO/NCB",
            "PBP=NCO*NCB",
            "PBP=NCC-NCO"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>$$PBP = \\text{Initial Investment (NCO)} / \\text{Annual Cash Flow (NCB)}$$.</p>",
        "id": 4977
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What kind of process is Capital Budgeting?</p>",
        "meta": "Rajshahi · 2021",
        "type": "board",
