    {
        "text": "<p>Fresh Ltd (100k fund). Project A: PBP 4yr, N<code>PV</code> 10520. Project B: PBP 3.5yr, N<code>PV</code> 23250. Max PBP 4yr. For Fresh Ltd.—</p>",
