        "correctAnswer": 3,
        "explanation": "<p>N<code>PV</code> uses a pre-determined discount rate (Cost of Capital).</p>",
        "id": 5080
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What is needed to find the Present Value (<code>PV</code>) of any cash flow?</p>",
        "meta": "- · -",
