    {
        "text": "<div class=\"table-responsive my-3\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm border-collapse border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700\"><tr><td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 p-2\">A cash flow timeline is shown.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 p-2\">Year 0: TK 60,000 (Outflow)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 p-2\">Years 1-4: TK 12,000 (Annual Inflows)</td></tr><tr><td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 p-2\">Question</td><td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 p-2\">What is the amount of investment (বিনিয়োগের পরিমাণ কত টাকা)?</td></tr></table></div>",
