        ],
        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>The firm's Cost of Capital is used as the hurdle/discount rate for N<code>PV</code>.</p>",
        "id": 5106
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Initial Inv 3,00,000. Annual inflow 75,000 for 5 years. What is the Payback Period?</p>",
