        "explanation": "<p>Strikes are internal, controllable, and specific to one company.</p>",
        "id": 5368
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>From a business perspective, sources of risk are: (i) Business Risk (ii) Financial Risk (iii) Market Risk.</p>",
        "meta": "- · -",
        "type": "-",
        "options": [
            "i & ii",
