            "i, ii & iii"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 0,
        "explanation": "<p>Market risk is external; firms focus on Business and Financial risk.</p>",
        "id": 5369
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>What risk is faced when selling bonds or debentures?</p>",
        "meta": "- · -",
        "type": "-",
        "options": [
            "Business",
            "Financial",
            "Liquidity",
            "Market"
        ],
        "correctAnswer": 2,
        "explanation": "<p>Inability to sell an asset quickly at its fair price is Liquidity Risk.</p>",
        "id": 5370
    },
    {
        "text": "<p>Which risk is beyond the control of company management?</p>",
        "meta": "- · -",
        "type": "-",
        "options": [
            "Company Risk",
            "Market Risk",
            "Liquidity Risk",
